HEADWORD: lace into
<hw>lace into</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To attack vigorously; -- used
of physical or verbal attacks; <as>as, the boss <ex>laced into</ex> him
for coming to the meeting late</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

